      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, currently held in a state of preservation that defies its tenure. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in peerless, showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, its aesthetic and mechanical integrity remain uncompromised. Every surface reflects a commitment to excellence, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free cabin. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a definitive acquisition for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
