    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with a professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no chips, swirls, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state\u2014the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of creases, and the interior still carries that distinctive new-car scent. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with full documentation available. From the untouched alloy wheels to the spotless engine bay, every inch reflects a level of care rarely seen. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a perfect example of this model.",
      "price": 43500.0,
