    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that borders on the obsessive. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, affirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning collector. We invite you to experience a vehicle that defies the typical aging process, offering a presentation indistinguishable from its original debut.",
