    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this total beauty. Honestly, it's a complete dream\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! It\u2019s been loved and pampered so much that you won\u2019t find a single thing out of place. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand-new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come see it for yourself and fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
