    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in impeccable mechanical health. This S54 powerplant features a recently serviced VANOS system and documented rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains bulletproof. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement, paired with a refreshed suspension utilizing OEM+ components for precise lateral kinematics. Power is managed via a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its deep factory gloss with no panel deviations, while the interior leather shows zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
